        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Minor Boon (Single-Use)</strong>: Torag repairs your equipment so you may continue your vigil.</p>\n<p>Once, a shield, weapon, or other item you hold or are wearing recovers all of its Hit Points. The item’s Hardness doubles for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>Torag can grant this boon just as the item would have been destroyed, preventing the item’s destruction.</p>\n<p>Occasionally, he grants this boon to restore an item important to dwarven history that has already been fully destroyed.</p>",
